      <div class="mt-10">
        <SupplierLogos />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 5: Areas -->
  <section class="section" style="background: var(--bg-light);">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="max-w-3xl fade-up">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: var(--navy);">
          Areas of Solihull Covered
        </h2>
        <p class="leading-relaxed mb-4" style="color: var(--text-soft);">
          Pindi covers the whole of the Solihull metropolitan borough and surrounding areas. He regularly works across:
        </p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-6">
          <div class="card p-5">
            <h3 class="font-bold mb-2" style="color: var(--navy);">Solihull Town &amp; B91</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-1 text-sm" style="color: var(--text-soft);">
              <li><strong>Solihull town centre</strong> — Large 1930s detached and semi-detached homes near Touchwood and Malvern Park</li>
              <li><strong>Shirley</strong> — Dense inter-war and post-war housing stock; a wide variety of kitchen sizes</li>
              <li><strong>Monkspath</strong> — Modern 1980s and 1990s executive housing with open-plan layouts</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="card p-5">
            <h3 class="font-bold mb-2" style="color: var(--navy);">Knowle, Dorridge &amp; B93</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-1 text-sm" style="color: var(--text-soft);">
              <li><strong>Knowle</strong> — Village character, substantial period and post-war detached homes on large plots</li>
              <li><strong>Dorridge</strong> — Executive detached homes, frequently extended; complex kitchen layouts common</li>
              <li><strong>Bentley Heath</strong> — Established residential area between Knowle and Solihull town</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="card p-5">
            <h3 class="font-bold mb-2" style="color: var(--navy);">New Developments</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-1 text-sm" style="color: var(--text-soft);">
              <li><strong>Dickens Heath</strong> — Contemporary village development; open-plan kitchen-diners with islands</li>
              <li><strong>Cheswick Green</strong> — Modern residential estate with standardised layouts and contemporary specifications</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="card p-5">
            <h3 class="font-bold mb-2" style="color: var(--navy);">Olton &amp; B92</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-1 text-sm" style="color: var(--text-soft);">
              <li><strong>Olton</strong> — Victorian and Edwardian properties, often with galley or extended-rear kitchens</li>
              <li><strong>Elmdon</strong> — Post-war family housing close to Birmingham Airport and the NEC</li>
              <li>All B92 postcodes covered</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--text-soft);">
          Visit the <a href="/areas/solihull/" class="font-semibold" style="color: var(--teal);">Solihull area page</a> for more detailed information, or call <a href="tel:07399651836" class="font-semibold" style="color: var(--teal);">07399 651836</a> to confirm your postcode is covered.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 6: What's Included & Pricing -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="max-w-3xl fade-up">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: var(--navy);">
          What's Included in a Solihull Kitchen Fit — and How Pricing Works
        </h2>
        <p class="leading-relaxed mb-4" style="color: var(--text-soft);">
          A full kitchen fitting service from Pindi Sahota covers the complete installation from stripped room to finished kitchen. This includes:
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 mb-6 pl-1" style="color: var(--text-soft);">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="mt-1 flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center" style="background: var(--teal); color: white; font-size: 0.65rem;">✓</span>
            <span>Stripping out the existing kitchen, including disconnecting the sink and removing appliances</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="mt-1 flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center" style="background: var(--teal); color: white; font-size: 0.65rem;">✓</span>
            <span>Levelling and setting out all base units to achieve a perfectly flat worktop run — critical in Solihull's older homes where floors can vary considerably</span>
